  <brief_title>Retrospective Study to Capture Dosing and Treatment Outcome Data in Subjects With Severe Congenital Protein C Deficiency Who Were Treated With Protein C Concentrate Under an Emergency Use IND</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Retrospective Study to Capture Dosing and Treatment Outcome Data in Subjects With Severe Congenital Protein C Deficiency Who Were Treated With Protein C Concentrate Under an Emergency Use IND</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Baxalta now part of Shire</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Shire</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a data collection study with the purpose of capturing dosing and treatment outcome
      data in subjects with severe congenital protein C deficiency who were treated with protein C
      concentrate under an Emergency Use Investigational New Drug Application (IND).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
