  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subject treated with protein C concentrate under a Baxter Healthcare Corporation
             Emergency Use IND

          -  Subject with diagnosis of severe congenital protein C deficiency

          -  Subject or parent/legally authorized representative has provided written informed
             consent
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
